cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper focuses on supervised hashing for image retrieval, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves deep learning techniques (cs.LG) and utilizes pairwise supervised information to guide both discrete coding and feature learning procedures (cs.AI). The evaluation is based on image retrieval performance (cs.IR) and the datasets used are related to multimedia (cs.MM).
